She grinned deviously, oh she had a plan alright! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 315<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/10/02 10:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=260.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://web.uvic.ca/grs/bowman/myth/images/haifa/h89.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bringers of Doom</span><hr size=1> &quot;Okay Athena, it shall be done.&quot; The God sent word to his messengers in his far off palace. The time in the grove seemed to pause as all the immortals sat in silence. The breeze sighed when nothing else seemd to make a sound at all.<br>
<br>
&quot;I've sent my word and Hypnos shall be brought before us. Athena, to break the mood, what have you been up to since before this council?&quot; <br>
