 <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uthegreatapollo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Great Apollo</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.maialino.it/musica/bsb_nick.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 179<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/10/02 2:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=260.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.efanguide.com/~hayden/gallery/misc/hayden28.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Getting the show on the road...</span><hr size=1> Apollo took a deep breath, inhaling the soft warm breeze that whipped trough the grove. His eyes darted around as he noticed everyone was in the same spot as if they'd been on Olympus. The summer sun shone magnificently though the scattered laurel and acasia trees. He turned his head to Poseidon.<br>
<br>
&quot;Well, if we're going to do this, we might as well do it in style.&quot; he smirked and spun around taking in the surroundings.<br>
<br>
He extended his hand to the left and three large marble stands were erected from the ground. To his right a small bench for Hypnos, and more for his associates. In the back, many thrones were placed, for an audiance if one was to attend. He walked away from his work, and the grove was still alive with more and more objects. It soon began to look like a outdoor courtroom.<br>
<br>
Now...we'll see if anyone wants to attend this little judicial extravaganza. He sat down and began to write a notice which would be sent out to all. <p>     *~*The Golden God*~*
