He then went over the the bench, took one of the long ends and flipped it over so it was no longer ocupying the space that it originally been in. He then snapped his fingers as black stone chair arose from the earth covered in a dark blue mose. He sat in it looking quiet bored with himself and almost feel asleep...***   <p>~*Thè göd ö §|èèp ãñd Ïñspîråõñ.*~  
